items.comment:
[BUG] Fix class not found compilation failure
### Motivation
 Fix compilation failure after merged
https://github.com/apache/bookkeeper/pull/2338

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20113411/83361037-3a8f4800-a3b8-11ea-9691-ea2842a18cfd.png)


### Changes
 Fix wrong package location.


 Reviewers: Matteo Minardi <minardi.matteo@hotmail.it>, Enrico Olivelli
<eolivelli@apache.org>
This closes #2351 from lamber-ken/misscleass

items.comment:
[BUG] Fix class not found compilation failure
### Motivation
 Fix compilation failure after merged
https://github.com/apache/bookkeeper/pull/2338

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20113411/83361037-3a8f4800-a3b8-11ea-9691-ea2842a18cfd.png)


### Changes
 Fix wrong package location.


 Reviewers: Matteo Minardi <minardi.matteo@hotmail.it>, Enrico Olivelli
<eolivelli@apache.org>
This closes #2351 from lamber-ken/misscleass
